89899,"uid":130228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9623e7bc1edb607e737721a29c6b24e63c9b9920","tid":1589899,"uid":34677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"睇相成部坦克車咁<br />\n咁同坦克有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"入面無人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"哦 原來係咁<br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040927897c884512d4414decf0f1d053ce0f45f6","tid":1589899,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13eaa90f0bfaaea8075572bc61d934ff89354667","tid":1589899,"uid":130228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9623e7bc1edb607e737721a29c6b24e63c9b9920","tid":1589899,"uid":34677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"睇相成部坦克車咁<br />\n咁同坦克有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"入面無人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"自走炮入面無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e937851b066a38f136a804cfde51672cb5a1c523","tid":1589899,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9623e7bc1edb607e737721a29c6b24e63c9b9920","tid":1589899,"uid":34677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"睇相成部坦克車咁<br />\n咁同坦克有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"坦克係上前線，對防禦同命中率都有好高要求<br />\n自走砲就set喺戰線後面，主要係做火力支援，對防禦同瞄準要求不高"},{"pid":"b53e462ab730fed23387d266ef79c82a6aa41ea0","tid":1589899,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9623e7bc1edb607e737721a29c6b24e63c9b9920","tid":1589899,"uid":34677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"睇相成部坦克車咁<br />\n咁同坦克有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"自走砲與戰車在外型上有相似之處，有些戰車的設計也以提供步兵火力支援為主要任務之一，但自走砲本質上仍與戰車不同。前者仍屬於後方支援的砲兵武器，只是可以自行驅動無須牽引。後者則是前線突擊武器。因此各方面作戰性能上雙方有不少區別。<br />\n<br />\n戰車對防禦要求很高，因此重量高、裝甲厚，以便抵抗敵方火力。自走砲因為主要部署在戰線後方，對防禦要求不高。裝甲只以防護機槍、小口徑機砲或者是砲彈近距離的碎片為目的。<br />\n戰車的戰車砲為了貫穿戰車裝甲，因此火砲砲口初速較高；自走砲則不需要。<br />\n戰車需要高命中率，因此瞄準系統精密。自走砲以間接瞄準的遠距離砲擊、火力覆蓋為主，對瞄準要求不高，有些自走砲並未配備直接瞄準用的瞄準具。<br />\n戰車不需要強調高仰角射擊能力；而自走砲為了追求火力覆蓋範圍，需要這方面的性能。<br />\n戰車多在前線地段直接作戰，需要應付瞬息萬變的戰況，對運動性能和砲口靈活度要求高；自走砲因為主要在後方進行火力支援，故只需重視火力，無須過分追求運動性能砲口靈活度。也因此不少自走砲只採用簡易的驅動系統，甚至沒有旋轉砲塔的設計。<br />\n自走砲大多彈藥下降時間長。"},{"pid":"36611e2b33b6670742e739cde107a0b1a6da2f1c","tid":1589899,"uid":130228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇相成部坦克車咁<br />\n咁同坦克有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><del>入面無人</del></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ead1703496fd59edda18856bccc03d358db93aad","tid":1589899,"uid":105387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:16:22.000Z","msg":"主要係買售後服務"},{"pid":"f29a5219fba5a6a3a238aaae5dd050a48e953ef2","tid":1589899,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"040927897c884512d4414decf0f1d053ce0f45f6","tid":1589899,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13eaa90f0bfaaea8075572bc61d934ff89354667","tid":1589899,"uid":130228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9623e7bc1edb607e737721a29c6b24e63c9b9920","tid":1589899,"uid":34677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"睇相成部坦克車咁<br />\n咁同坦克有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"入面無人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"自走炮入面無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"屌 自走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}